translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 南の連中にも連絡して…………」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Contact the guys in the south as well..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ク。ククク、ク」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ku. Kukuku, ku."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「どーーーこへ……逃げようってんだ……？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Whe-re... do you plan to run away to...?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「この魔王様が……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "This Demon King...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: わざわざ出向いてやったってのによぉ……！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: even took the trouble to come personally...!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 地響きを鳴らし、巨体を揺らし。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Causing the ground to rumble, shaking its massive body.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人でさえない何かに変じた怪物が、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A monster transformed into something not even a demon,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスを睨みつけていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: was glaring at Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「こいつがケイブリス……だと……？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "This is Caviris... is it...?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お、おぉ、きい……っ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "O-oh, kii..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……はい。魔人の時より、更に……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Yes. Even more than when it was a demon..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……ふん。気色の悪い姿になりやがって」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Hmph. It’s taken on a disgusting form."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ずいぶん急いで来たではないか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You came in quite a hurry, didn’t you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 奇襲すれば俺様に勝てるとでも思ったか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Did you really think you could win against me by a surprise attack?"
"...In a hurry...? Surprise attack...?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「…………ふっ、ふはっ、ぐぁははは、っ…………
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Huh, huhah, guahahaha..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぶわぁぁぁーーーーーーっははははははははは！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Buwahhhhhh—hahahahahahahaha!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぐぁはははははははははははは！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Guahahahahahahahahahaha!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうか！　お前ら的には急いでたのか、俺様は！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I see! You guys thought *I* was in a hurry!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちょいと散歩のつもりだったのによぉ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I was just thinking of taking a little stroll!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「こいつはな、ただの試運転だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "This here is just a test run.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 身体を進化させた時と同じだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It’s the same as when I evolved my body.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうなったか、馴染ませなきゃならねえ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have to get used to how it’s turned out."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「その先に、ちょうどチョロチョロしてやがる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ahead of that, I just happened to pick on you guys scurrying about.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: てめぇらを選んでやっただけの話だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That’s all there is to it."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「鼻息ひとつで終わっちまったら困るからよぉ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If it ended with just a sniff, that would be boring,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いい感じに楽しめればと思ったが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I thought I’d enjoy this properly, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: さっきの人間共はあっさりだったしなあ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Those humans from earlier went down too easily."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ベラベラベラベラ良く喋る野郎だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You’re a real chatterbox.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 叩き斬ってやるから黙って死ね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I’ll slash you down, so shut up and die."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぎゃああぁっはははははははは！！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gyaaaah hahahahahaha!!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まあそう言うなよおお！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, don’t say that!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 努力が実ったらよ、過程を語りたくなるだろ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When your effort pays off, you want to talk about the process, right!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「これまで生き残るのにも強くなるのにも、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Up until now, to survive and to become stronger,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 苦労ばっかりの人生よ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: it’s been a life full of hardships.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何度も何度も殺されそうにもなったし……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Many times I was almost killed over and over...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「魔人になったってぇのに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Even though I became a demon,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王って奴はいつまでも目の前にちらついて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: that Demon King keeps haunting me right in front of me,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺の邪魔をしやがる」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: always getting in my way."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さっきだってそうだぜ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It was just like that earlier too.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リトルプリンセスを叩き殺すのも……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Killing the Little Princess too...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まぁぁぁったく、苦労したもんだぜ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Man, that was a real struggle."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「何度ブン殴っても、恋人の名前を何度も呼びながら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "No matter how many times I punched him, he kept sobbing while calling his lover’s name again and again.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 啜り泣くんだぜ？　幽霊かなんかかっての。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sobbing like that—was he a ghost or something?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 犯しながらだから、気晴らしはできたがよぉ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, since I was violating him, it was a bit of a distraction!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「よし分かった、黙れとは言わん。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Alright, I get it. I’m not telling you to shut up.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 精々喋りながら…………
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At most, keep talking while...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぐッ！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Guh!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 進み出そうとしたランスが、片膝をつく。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance, who tried to step forward, drops to one knee.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "This here is just a test run.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 身体を進化させた時と同じだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It’s the same as when I evolved my body.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうなったか、馴染ませなきゃならねえ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have to get used to how it’s turned out."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「その先に、ちょうどチョロチョロしてやがる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ahead of that, I just happened to pick on you guys scurrying about.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: てめぇらを選んでやっただけの話だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That’s all there is to it."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「鼻息ひとつで終わっちまったら困るからよぉ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If it ended with just a sniff, that would be boring,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いい感じに楽しめればと思ったが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I thought I’d enjoy this properly, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: さっきの人間共はあっさりだったしなあ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Those humans from earlier went down too easily."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ベラベラベラベラ良く喋る野郎だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You’re a real chatterbox.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 叩き斬ってやるから黙って死ね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I’ll slash you down, so shut up and die."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぎゃああぁっはははははははは！！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gyaaaah hahahahahaha!!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まあそう言うなよおお！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, don’t say that!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 努力が実ったらよ、過程を語りたくなるだろ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When your effort pays off, you want to talk about the process, right!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「これまで生き残るのにも強くなるのにも、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Up until now, to survive and to become stronger,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 苦労ばっかりの人生よ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: it’s been a life full of hardships.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何度も何度も殺されそうにもなったし……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Many times I was almost killed over and over...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「魔人になったってぇのに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Even though I became a demon,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王って奴はいつまでも目の前にちらついて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: that Demon King keeps haunting me right in front of me,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺の邪魔をしやがる」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: always getting in my way."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さっきだってそうだぜ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It was just like that earlier too.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リトルプリンセスを叩き殺すのも……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Killing the Little Princess too...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まぁぁぁったく、苦労したもんだぜ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Man, that was a real struggle."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「何度ブン殴っても、恋人の名前を何度も呼びながら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "No matter how many times I punched him, he kept sobbing while calling his lover’s name again and again.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 啜り泣くんだぜ？　幽霊かなんかかっての。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sobbing like that—was he a ghost or something?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 犯しながらだから、気晴らしはできたがよぉ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, since I was violating him, it was a bit of a distraction!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「よし分かった、黙れとは言わん。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Alright, I get it. I’m not telling you to shut up.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 精々喋りながら…………
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At most, keep talking while...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぐッ！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Guh!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 進み出そうとしたランスが、片膝をつく。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance, who tried to step forward, drops to one knee.
